page1.title: Hello!
page1.content: I’m Vinay Kudari, currently pursuing MSc in Computer Science at SUNY Buffalo University. I’m very enthusiastic to learn about Machine Learning and Deep Learning techniques. . Previously, I was a Software Developer at Brave Orbit saw it grow from team of 3 to 20. Before that I worked as a Big Data Analyst at Accenture . I graduated from National Institute of Technology, Durgapur with B.Tech in Computer Science where I worked on thesis by title Gender Classification Using Convolutional Neural Networks supervised by Dakshina Ranjan Kisku. I also spent good amount of time in designing flyers/posters for college festivals. . Mail Twitter LinkedIn GitHub Medium .
